data.description: This move in ready two story home is a must see! The home has an inviting front covered porch that would be great for sitting and enjoying the outdoors. It's a 2600 square foot, 4 bedroom 2 bath home with a detached oversized garage! Upon entering you find open concept floor plan. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances that stay with the home and a wrap around peninsula. It has a dining area right off of the kitchen that overlooks the large living room. In the main floor you find 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom. Upstairs is a large bedroom, and a sitting area accompanied by a full bathroom. The home sits on a corner lot has a nice back patio to enjoy sitting outside. The home has had many updates over the past couple of years including new door frames in 2022, water heater 2018, new laminated hardwood flooring in 2018, the roof and gutters with replaced in 2017 on the garage and house. It has a new retaining wall in 2023, some new windows in 2023, new concrete patio and steps, fresh paint in 2023. Move in ready!
